# Career Intelligence Dashboard

> Toronto job market, decoded.

Transform 50,000+ monthly job postings into three actionable insights.

## Quick Start


## Data Sources
| Source | Licence | Frequency | Geographic Granularity |
|--------|---------|-----------|------------------------|
| Job Bank Postings | Open Government Licence - Canada | Monthly | Toronto CMA + GTA municipalities |
| Job Bank Wages | Open Government Licence - Canada | Annual | Economic Region (Toronto 3530) |
| StatsCan JVWS (14-10-0444-01) | Statistics Canada Open Licence | Quarterly | Economic Region |
| Indeed Hiring Lab (GitHub) | CC-BY-4.0 | Daily/Weekly | Provincial (Ontario) |
| Lightcast Open Skills | Free registration | Continuous | 34K+ skill taxonomy |

